Real-World Uses of AI for Better Video Coding
Artificial Intelligence is increasingly being integrated into modern video coding systems to improve:
Compression efficiency
Visual quality
Streaming stability
Low-latency delivery
Bandwidth optimization

AI is now used in:
Streaming platforms
Cloud gaming
Video conferencing
Automotive systems
Surveillance
Smartphones
Broadcasting

Main Areas Where AI Improves Video Coding
AI in Video Coding
│
├── Encoding Optimization
├── Perceptual Quality Enhancement
├── Bitrate Control
├── Super-Resolution
├── Artifact Removal
